TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: IIF(NOT ISNULL(WRT_DISTRICT_CODE) AND NOT ISNULL(WRT_AGENCY_CODE) AND WRT_DISTRICT_CODE<>WRT_AGENCY_CODE,TRUE,FALSE)

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT WRI_AGENT_CODE AS WRI_AGENT_CODE, AGENT_CLASS_CODE AS AGENT_CLASS_CODE, AGENCY_CODE AS AGENCY_CODE, AGENCY_LEADER AS AGENCY_LEADER, AGENCY_LEADER_TITLE AS AGENCY_LEADER_TITLE, DISTRICT_CODE AS DISTRICT_CODE, DISTRICT_LEADER AS DISTRICT_LEADER, DISTRICT_LEADER_TITLE AS DISTRICT_LEADER_TITLE, THIRD_PARTY_COMPANY_CODE AS THIRD_PARTY_COMPANY_CODE, POLICYNO AS POLICYNO, THIRD_PARTY_AGENT_CODE AS THIRD_PARTY_AGENT_CODE, CONSOLIDATED_COMMISSION_DATE AS CONSOLIDATED_COMMISSION_DATE, CALLIDUS_COMPENSATION_DATE AS CALLIDUS_COMPENSATION_DATE FROM IN_TP_POLICY_MASTER

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_RECORD_NO, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_COMP_CD, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DTE_TXN_PROCESS_DATE, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DTE_CONSOLIDATED_DATE, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_LEV1_CD, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_3RDPARTY_CD, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_3RDPARTY_SHORTCD, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_POLICY_NO, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_POLICY_HOLDER, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_POLICY_TYPE, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_COMPONENT_NO, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_POLICY_TERM, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_CURR_CD, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_INSURED_SUM, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DTE_INCEPTION_DATE, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DTE_PREM_DUE, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DTE_PAID_TO, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_BILL_FREQ, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_PREMIUM, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_EXTRA_LOADING, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_FEE_TYPE, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_BASIC_COMM, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_COMM_OR, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_EXTRACOMM_OR, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_COMM_TF, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_COMM_PAS, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_COMM_OTHER, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_FX_RATE, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_COMM_TOTAL, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_POLICY_YEAR, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_COMM_RATE, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_EXPECTED_TTCOMM, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_DIFF_TTCOMM, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_AgtCOMM_SplitRate, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_AgtEarn_Comm, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_LDR_OR_TTRate, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.DEC_LDR_OR_TT, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_DR_COMMEXP_ILACC, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_CR_AGTBALANCE_ACC, IN_ST_SINGLIFE.TXT_COMM_GST_ACC, IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_STRING, IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_FILE_NAME, IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_VALUE FROM IN_ST_TP_CMTX, IN_ETL_CONTROL WHERE IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'CMTX_CYCLE_DATE' AND IN_ETL_CONTROL.DEC_RUNNING_FLG = 1 AND IN_ETL_CONTROL.TXT_FILE_NAME ='$$STR_TP_FILE_NAME'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT DISTINCT CS_BUSINESSUNIT.NAME AS BU_NAME, AGT.GENERICATTRIBUTE1 AS AGENCY_CODE, 'SGY'||AGT.GENERICATTRIBUTE1 AS AGENCY, AGT.NAME AS POS_NAME, AGT.GENERICATTRIBUTE4 AS COMM_AGT_CLASSCODE, AGT.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS EFF_ST, AGT.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS EFF_END, cs_payee.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS PAYEE_EFF_ST, cs_payee.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS PAYEE_EFF_END, AGY.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE AS AGY_EFF_ST, AGY.EFFECTIVEENDDATE AS AGY_EFF_END, cs_TITLE.NAME as AGY_TITLE, CASE WHEN cs_TITLE.NAME='DISTRICT' OR cs_TITLE.NAME='ORGANISATION' THEN '1' ELSE '0' END AS AGY_IS_DISTRICT_FLAG FROM CS_POSITION AGT INNER JOIN cs_payee ON AGT.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE ('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND cs_payee.removedate = TO_DATE ('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND AGT.payeeseq = cs_payee.payeeseq INNER JOIN CS_BUSINESSUNIT ON CS_BUSINESSUNIT.MASK = cs_payee.BUSINESSUNITMAP AND CS_BUSINESSUNIT.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ = AGT.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ INNER JOIN CS_POSITION AGY ON 'SGY'||AGT.GENERICATTRIBUTE1 = AGY.NAME AND AGY.removedate = TO_DATE ('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') INNER JOIN CS_TITLE ON AGY.TITLESEQ = CS_TITLE.RULEELEMENTOWNERSEQ AND CS_TITLE.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE ('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS')

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: POS_NAME = LOOKUP_AGENT AND PAYEE_EFF_ST <= LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND PAYEE_EFF_END > LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND EFF_ST <= LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND EFF_END > LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND AGY_EFF_ST <= LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT AND AGY_EFF_END > LOOKUP_CONSOLIDATED_DT
